705577f-b.text:
Marcy Avenue, north from Monroe Street, showing a W. P. A. street improvement project. In the left foreground, at the S. W. corner of Gates Avenue, is St. Georges Church. View 2 shows the avenue, north from Quincy Street
and the "E1" on Lexington Avenue.
June 27, 1935
Views 1,2
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
